Demo: Pizza Class

- Pete's Pizza offers a variety of pizza types, sizes, and options
- Three basic types: Cheese, Pepperoni, and Veggie
- Pete's usually makes their pizzas with their famous hand-tossed
  crust, but thin crust is available upon request
- Pizza sizes are as follows: Small (9"), Medium (12"), Large (16"),
  and XL (18")
- Special instructions may be included (e.g., "no bell peppers")

